#. <section id="vagga"><section class="sutta" data-uid="an1.296" id="296"><article><div class="hgroup"><p class="division">
msgctxt "an1.296-305:0.1"
msgid "Aṅguttara Nikāya 1"
msgstr "Numbered Discourses 1"

#. </p><p>
#. VAR: aparā ekadhammādipāḷi (s1) | aparā ekadhammādipāli (s2, s3)
msgctxt "an1.296-305:0.2"
msgid "24. Paṭhamavagga"
msgstr "24. First"

#. </p><h1>
msgctxt "an1.296-305:0.3"
msgid "296"
msgstr "296"

#. </h1></div><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc296.1"></a>
msgctxt "an1.296-305:296.1.1"
msgid ""
"“Ekadhammo, bhikkhave, bhāvito bahulīkato ekantanibbidāya virāgāya nirodhāya "
"upasamāya abhiññāya sambodhāya nibbānāya saṃvattati."
msgstr ""
"“One thing, mendicants, when developed and cultivated, leads solely to "
"disillusionment, dispassion, cessation, peace, insight, awakening, and "
"extinguishment."

msgctxt "an1.296-305:296.1.2"
msgid "Katamo ekadhammo?"
msgstr "What one thing?"

msgctxt "an1.296-305:296.1.3"
msgid "Buddhānussati."
msgstr "Recollection of the Buddha."

msgctxt "an1.296-305:296.1.4"
msgid ""
"Ayaṃ kho, bhikkhave, ekadhammo bhāvito bahulīkato ekantanibbidāya virāgāya "
"nirodhāya upasamāya abhiññāya sambodhāya nibbānāya saṃvattatī”ti."
msgstr ""
"This one thing, when developed and cultivated, leads solely to "
"disillusionment, dispassion, cessation, peace, insight, awakening, and "
"extinguishment.”"

#. </p></article></section><section class="sutta" data-uid="an1.297" id="297"><article><div class="hgroup"><h1>
msgctxt "an1.296-305:296.1.5"
msgid "297–​305"
msgstr "297–​305"

#. </h1></div><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc297.1"></a>
msgctxt "an1.296-305:297.1.1"
msgid ""
"“Ekadhammo, bhikkhave, bhāvito bahulīkato ekantanibbidāya virāgāya nirodhāya "
"upasamāya abhiññāya sambodhāya nibbānāya saṃvattati."
msgstr ""
"“One thing, mendicants, when developed and cultivated leads solely to "
"disillusionment, dispassion, cessation, peace, insight, awakening, and "
"extinguishment."

msgctxt "an1.296-305:297.1.2"
msgid "Katamo ekadhammo?"
msgstr "What one thing?"

msgctxt "an1.296-305:297.1.3"
msgid ""
"Dhammānussati … pe … saṅghānussati … sīlānussati … cāgānussati … "
"devatānussati … ānāpānassati … maraṇassati … kāyagatāsati … upasamānussati."
msgstr ""
"Recollection of the teaching … Recollection of the Saṅgha … Recollection of "
"ethical conduct … Recollection of generosity … Recollection of the deities … "
"Mindfulness of breathing … Mindfulness of death … Mindfulness of the body … "
"Recollection of peace."

msgctxt "an1.296-305:297.1.4"
msgid ""
"Ayaṃ kho, bhikkhave, ekadhammo bhāvito bahulīkato ekantanibbidāya virāgāya "
"nirodhāya upasamāya abhiññāya sambodhāya nibbānāya saṃvattatī”ti."
msgstr ""
"This one thing, when developed and cultivated, leads solely to "
"disillusionment, dispassion, cessation, peace, insight, awakening, and "
"extinguishment.”"

#. </p><p class="endsection">
msgctxt "an1.296-305:297.1.5"
msgid "Vaggo paṭhamo."
msgstr ""
